This repository contains teaching materials authored by Dr. Hildegard Haas
for the BCOBM214 Entrepreneurship & Business Development course at
EU Business School. The materials include — without limitation — written
text, structured framework data, HTML/CSS/JavaScript, and visual layouts.

The materials are made available for the personal academic use of enrolled
BCOBM214 students and the professional use of EU Business School faculty.

