- Reading and viewing the materials in their hosted form
- Personal note-taking from the materials for the purpose of study
- Citation of the materials in academic work, with full attribution to
  Dr. Hildegard Haas, EU Business School, and the appropriate framework author(s)
- Use by EU Business School faculty for course delivery

NOT PERMITTED WITHOUT PRIOR WRITTEN PERMISSION
- Reproduction or republication of any substantial part of the materials,
  in print or digital form, for purposes other than personal study
- Redistribution, mirroring or hosting on third-party platforms
- Use in any commercial product, training programme or consultancy offering
- Creation of derivative works based on the structure, layout, or framework
  selection of the Slibrary system
- Removal or alteration of the copyright notices, footers or attributions

